          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Commodity Delivery Relief Act - Amends the Commodity Exchange Act to revise the exclusion from the definition of &quot;swap&quot; of any sale of a nonfinancial commodity or security for deferred shipment or delivery, so long as the transaction is intended to be physically settled.</p> <p>Excludes from the meaning of &quot;swap&quot; also: (1) any purchase of a nonfinancial commodity or security for deferred shipment or delivery, so long as the transaction is intended to be physically settled; and (2) any stand-alone or embedded option for which exercise results in a physical delivery obligation.</p>]]></text>
        </item>
